Package: mazing
Title: Utilities for making and plotting mazes
Version: 0.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Kelly", 
           family = "Street", 
           email = "street.kelly@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           comment = "0000-0001-6379-5013")
Description: This package provides utilities for generating and plotting random mazes. The mazes are based on matrices, so can only consist of vertical and horizontal lines along a regular grid. But there is no need to use every possible space, so they can take on many different shapes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    graphics,
    methods,
    stats
